The paper also involves the use of deep learning methods, which makes it likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. 

As the paper discusses the effectiveness of pre-trained image features, it could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. 

The use of rendering techniques for generating synthetic images could place the paper in the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category. 

Finally, the paper's focus on object detection could also place it in the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category, as object detection is a crucial task in robotics applications.
